OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1775664666
OL,3,CKatie Price given seventh driving ban
OL,4,Cover 80mph speeding ticket
OL,6,FKatie Price has been banned from
OL,7,Fdriving for the seventh time after
OL,8,Ffailing to respond to police letters
OL,9,Fabout an 80mph speeding ticket.
OL,11,FThe former glamour model, 47, was
OL,12,Fcontacted after a Ford Capri
OL,13,Fregistered in her name was caught
OL,14,Fspeeding on the A64 near to the North
OL,15,FYorkshire village of Stutton.
OL,17,FAfter failing to respond, she was
OL,18,Fgiven a six-month driving ban and
OL,19,Flegal costs of more than #1,000.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
