PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1775664666
OL,3,CKatie Price given seventh driving ban
OL,4,Cover 80mph speeding ticket
OL,6,FPrice, who lives in West Sussex, has
OL,7,Fnow received bans totalling more than
OL,8,Fsix years since she was first
OL,9,Fdisqualified in 2010.
OL,11,FIn 2021, a judge condemned her for
OL,12,F"one of the worst driving records I
OL,13,Fhave ever seen", as she was given a 16-
OL,14,Fweek suspended prison sentence for
OL,15,Fdrink-driving while disqualified and
OL,16,Fwithout insurance.
OL,18,F"You appear to think you are above the
OL,19,Flaw," District Judge Amanda Kelly told
OL,20,Fher at the time.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@OO]zD@AOU{D@EO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
