FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1775664666
OL,3,CKatie Price given seventh driving ban
OL,4,Cover 80mph speeding ticket
OL,6,FPrice's latest conviction was dealt
OL,7,Fwith last week in the Single Justice
OL,8,FProcedure, a secretive court process
OL,9,Fwhere magistrates deal with criminal
OL,10,Fcases behind closed doors.
OL,12,FCourt papers show Price was charged
OL,13,Fwith speeding and failing to give
OL,14,Finformation relating to the
OL,15,Fidentification of the driver of a
OL,16,Fvehicle.
OL,18,FThe Ford Capri was caught on a speed
OL,19,Fcamera on a 70mph stretch of the A64
OL,20,Fat 3.03pm on 15 October last year.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1775664666
OL,3,CKatie Price given seventh driving ban
OL,4,Cover 80mph speeding ticket
OL,6,FShe was sent a police letter about the
OL,7,Fincident five days later, followed by
OL,8,Fa reminder.
OL,10,FThe force said no response was
OL,11,Freceived to either letter.
OL,13,FMagistrate Claire Sagar, sitting at
OL,14,FHarrogate Magistrates' Court last
OL,15,FTuesday, found Price guilty of failing
OL,16,Fto respond to police, ordering her to
OL,17,Fpay a #660 fine, #120 in costs, and a
OL,18,F#264 victim surcharge.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
