FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1775664666
OL,3,CKatie Price given seventh driving ban
OL,4,Cover 80mph speeding ticket
OL,6,FDue to the secretive nature of the
OL,7,Fcourt process, it is not known if
OL,8,FPrice was given the chance to argue
OL,9,Fagainst another driving ban or whether
OL,10,Fthe court knew of her previous driving
OL,11,Frecord. The records do not reveal if
OL,12,Fshe already had penalty points on her
OL,13,Flicence.
OL,15,FThe speeding charge was withdrawn by
OL,16,Fthe police.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
