PN,36607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1775664666
OL,3,CKatie Price given seventh driving ban
OL,4,Cover 80mph speeding ticket
OL,6,FBankruptcies from 2019 and 2024 have
OL,7,Fbeen discharged, but she remains the
OL,8,Fsubject of a court order aimed at
OL,9,Fsettling her debts until February 2027.
OL,11,FSpeaking on a podcast last year, Price
OL,12,Fsaid she now struggles to obtain car
OL,13,Finsurance due to her litany of past
OL,14,Fdriving convictions.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
